OL,3,C'Forensic grease' helps catch stalker
OL,4,Crepeatedly visiting victim's house
OL,6,F'Forensic grease' has been used for
OL,7,Fthe first time by police in Kent to
OL,8,Forder to catch a stalker who kept
OL,9,Fvisiting his victim's home.
OL,11,FThe grease was applied to the windows
OL,12,Fof the stalking victim's home, after
OL,13,Fthe man they had a restraining order
OL,14,Fagainst had been released from prison.
OL,16,FThe substance is usually used to
OL,17,Fdetect thieves and shows up under
OL,18,Fultra-violet light which allows police
OL,19,Fto see who has come into contact with
OL,20,Fan object.
