OL,3,C'Forensic grease' helps catch stalker
OL,4,Crepeatedly visiting victim's house
OL,6,FHowever in a first for Kent Police,
OL,7,Fthey trialled it as part of a test
OL,8,Fpilot to help victims of domestic
OL,9,Fabuse and stalking.
OL,11,FOn 10 April, officers were called to a
OL,12,Freport that a man had been seen near
OL,13,Fthe victim's property in Ashford.
OL,15,FThe man fled the scene but on the 18
OL,16,FApril, officers found the man at the
OL,17,Fvictim's address and he was arrested.
OL,19,FTests on a body warmer he was wearing
OL,20,Fshowed traces of the forensic grease
OL,21,Fwhich had been applied to the windows.
