OL,3,C'Forensic grease' helps catch stalker
OL,4,Crepeatedly visiting victim's house
OL,6,FMarley Edmed, 25, formerly of Laurens
OL,7,FVan Der Post Way, Ashford, was charged
OL,8,Fwith two counts of breaching a
OL,9,Frestraining order and jailed for 46
OL,10,Fweeks after admitting both offences at
OL,11,FFolkestone Magistrates' Court on 19
OL,12,FApril.
OL,14,FDetective Inspector Zoe Wilczek, of
OL,15,Fthe East Kent Proactive Domestic Abuse
OL,16,FTeam, said: "Our number one priority
OL,17,Fis protecting victims of stalking,
OL,18,Fharassment and domestic violence and
OL,19,Fwe will use any means open to us to
OL,20,Fachieve this.
