OL,3,C'Forensic grease' helps catch stalker
OL,4,Crepeatedly visiting victim's house
OL,6,F"I believe this case is the first in
OL,7,Fthe county in which this forensic
OL,8,Fgrease has been used in a domestic
OL,9,Fabuse investigation, strengthening the
OL,10,Fcase which secured a conviction at
OL,11,Fcourt, and I am pleased it has helped
OL,12,Fus swiftly put this repeat offender
OL,13,Fbehind bars.
OL,15,F"We now know this forensic marking
OL,16,Fmethod of protection is effective and
OL,17,Fwe will continue to utilise it in
OL,18,Fdomestic abuse and stalking
OL,19,Fsafeguarding methods."
